title: Lowest Female Suicide Mortality Rate
description: In 2021, Oman's female suicide mortality rate was the lowest globally at 0.21 per 100,000 female population, indicating strong mental health support systems.

title: High Employment in Industry
description: As of 2023, 40.16% of Oman's total employment is in the industrial sector, showcasing a robust industrial workforce.

title: Rapid Population Growth
description: Oman's population growth rate reached 6.53% in 2023, one of the highest globally, reflecting a rapidly expanding population.

title: Significant Urban Population Growth
description: In 2023, Oman's urban population growth was 7.27%, indicating a swift urbanization trend.

title: High Dependence on Arab World Imports
description: In 2023, 53.13% of Oman's merchandise imports came from the Arab World, highlighting a strong regional trade reliance.
